7372 - Prepackaged Software Summary > FLEETMATICS AUSTRALIA PTY. LTD. (formerly FLEETMATICS AUSTRALIA PTY. LTD.) is an Australian proprietary company. Its operations cover prepackaged software. The company is not involved in the import or export of goods. FLEETMATICS AUSTRALIA PTY. LTD. is headquartered in Pyrmont, New South Wales. It is headed by director Darren James Day. For the 2024 financial year, the company reported revenue of $33.54 million. Its net profit totalled $891,000. FLEETMATICS AUSTRALIA PTY. LTD. forms part of the services industry sector.
